全空间的任意无穷小旋转 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{\delta}\vec{\varphi}$
\end_inset

 引起的位移和速度分别为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathrm{\delta}\vec{r}_{i}=\mathrm{\delta}\vec{\varphi}\cross\vec{r}_{i}\qquad\mathrm{\delta}\vec{v}_{i}=\mathrm{\delta}\vec{\varphi}\cross\vec{v}_{i}\qquad\forall i\in\{1,\dots,n\}
\]

\end_inset

它们不改变系统的力学行为，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}0=\mathrm{\delta}L & =\sum_{i=1}^{n}\pdv{L}{\vec{r}_{i}}\vdot\mathrm{\delta}\vec{r}_{i}+\sum_{i=1}^{n}\pdv{L}{\vec{v}_{i}}\vdot\mathrm{\delta}\vec{v}_{i}\\
 & =\sum_{i=1}^{n}\dot{\vec{p}}_{i}\vdot\left(\mathrm{\delta}\vec{\varphi}\cross\vec{r}_{i}\right)+\sum_{i=1}^{n}\vec{p}_{i}\vdot\left(\mathrm{\delta}\vec{\varphi}\cross\vec{v}_{i}\right)\\
 & =\mathrm{\delta}\vec{\varphi}\vdot\sum_{i=1}^{n}\dv{}{t}\left(\vec{r}_{i}\cross\vec{p}_{i}\right)\eqqcolon\mathrm{\delta}\vec{\varphi}\vdot\sum_{i=1}^{n}\dv{\vec{L}_{i}}{t}
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

故 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{L}\coloneqq\sum_{i=1}^{n}\vec{L}_{i}$
\end_inset

 为一守恒量，名为质点系的
\color blue
角动量 (angular momentum)
\color inherit
；其中 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{L}_{i}=\vec{r}_{i}\cross\vec{p}_{i}$
\end_inset

 为
\color blue
第 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

 个质点的角动量
\color inherit
。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Chapter
Hamiltonian 力学
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Hamilton's 方程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Legendre's 变换
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Lagrangian 函数 
\begin_inset Formula $L(\underline{q},\underline{\dot{q}},t)$
\end_inset

 关于
\color blue
广义速度
\color inherit
的导数被称为
\color blue
广义动量
\color inherit
，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\underline{p}\coloneqq\begin{bmatrix}p_{1} & \dots & p_{n}\end{bmatrix}\coloneqq\begin{bmatrix}\dfrac{\partial L}{\partial\dot{q}_{1}} & \dots & \dfrac{\partial L}{\partial\dot{q}_{n}}\end{bmatrix}\eqqcolon\pdv{}{\underline{\dot{q}}}L(\underline{q},\underline{\dot{q}},t)
\]

\end_inset

上述定义式右端是以 
\begin_inset Formula $(\underline{q},\underline{\dot{q}},t)$
\end_inset

 为自变量的（代数）表达式。若将 
\begin_inset Formula $(\underline{q},t)$
\end_inset

 及左端的 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{p}$
\end_inset

 视为已知量，而将 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{\dot{q}}$
\end_inset

 视为未知量，则该定义式可视为关于 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{\dot{q}}$
\end_inset

 的（代数）方程。从中解得 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{\dot{q}}=\underline{\dot{q}}(\underline{q},\underline{p},t)$
\end_inset

，便可将 
\begin_inset Formula $L(\underline{q},\underline{\dot{q}},t)$
\end_inset

 也化作以 
\begin_inset Formula $(\underline{q},\underline{p},t)$
\end_inset

 为自变量的表达式，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\tilde{L}(\underline{q},\underline{p},t)\coloneqq\mathopen{L}\left(\underline{q},\underline{\dot{q}}(\underline{q},\underline{p},t),t\right)
\]

\end_inset

由此可定义 
\color blue
Hamiltonian 函数
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{H(\underline{q},\underline{p},t)\coloneqq\underline{p}\cdot\underline{\dot{q}}(\underline{q},\underline{p},t)-\tilde{L}(\underline{q},\underline{p},t)}
\]

\end_inset

其物理意义为系统的
\color blue
能量
\color inherit
。上述由 
\begin_inset Formula $L(\underline{q},\underline{\dot{q}},t)$
\end_inset

 导出 
\begin_inset Formula $H(\underline{q},\underline{p},t)$
\end_inset

 的过程在数学上被称为 
\color blue
Legendre's 变换
\color inherit
。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Hamilton's 方程
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "sec:Hamilton's-方程"

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $H(\underline{q},\underline{p},t)$
\end_inset

 的全微分可写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dd{H}=\dd{(\underline{p}\cdot\underline{\dot{q}}-\tilde{L})}=\underline{p}\cdot\dd{\underline{\dot{q}}}+\underline{\dot{q}}\cdot\dd{\underline{p}}-\pdv{L}{\underline{q}}\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}-\pdv{L}{\underline{\dot{q}}}\cdot\dd{\underline{\dot{q}}}-\pdv{L}{t}\dd{t}
\]

\end_inset

利用 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{p}$
\end_inset

 的定义及 Lagrange's 方程，可得
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dd{H}=\pdv{H}{\underline{p}}\cdot\dd{\underline{p}}+\pdv{H}{\underline{q}}\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}+\pdv{H}{t}\dd{t}=\underline{\dot{q}}\cdot\dd{\underline{p}}-\underline{\dot{p}}\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}-\pdv{L}{t}\dd{t}
\]

\end_inset

比较后一个等号两侧 
\begin_inset Formula $\dd{\underline{p}},\dd{\underline{q}}$
\end_inset

 系数，即得 
\color blue
Hamilton's 方程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{\underline{\dot{q}}=+\pdv{H}{\underline{p}}\qquad\underline{\dot{p}}=-\pdv{H}{\underline{q}}}
\]

\end_inset

此方程只含一阶导数，且具有很好的对称性，在分析力学中居于核心地位，故又名
\color blue
正则方程 (canonical equations)
\color inherit
。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
能量守恒
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "sec:Hamiltonian-能量守恒"

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
比较 
\begin_inset Formula $\dd{t}$
\end_inset

 两侧的系数，可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{\pdv{H}{t}=-\pdv{L}{t}}
\]

\end_inset

其中表示
\color blue
时间
\color inherit
的变量 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

 可以推广为除了 
\begin_inset Formula $p,q$
\end_inset

 以外的任何决定 
\begin_inset Formula $L,H$
\end_inset

 的参数。利用 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand nameref
reference "sec:Hamilton's-方程"

\end_inset

，可以将
\color blue
能量守恒
\color inherit
条件化为
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dv{H}{t}=\cancel{\underline{\dot{q}}\cdot\dv{\underline{p}}{t}-\underline{\dot{p}}\cdot\dv{\underline{q}}{t}}+\boxed{\pdv{H}{t}=0}
\]

\end_inset

即 
\color blue

\begin_inset Formula $H$
\end_inset

 不显含时间
\color inherit
。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
作用量的 Hamiltonian 形式
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
边界条件的作用
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "sec:边界条件的作用"

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
真实运动所对应的作用量 
\begin_inset Formula $S=\int_{t_{1}}^{t_{2}}L(\underline{q},\underline{\dot{q}},t)\dd{t}$
\end_inset

 可以被视为由始末时刻 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{1},t_{2}$
\end_inset

 及位置 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{q}(t_{1}),\underline{q}(t_{2})$
\end_inset

 所确定的量，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S=\mathopen{S}\left(\underline{q}(t_{1}),\underline{q}(t_{2}),t_{1},t_{2}\right)
\]

\end_inset

若固定 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{1},t_{2}$
\end_inset

 但允许 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{q}(t_{1}),\underline{q}(t_{2})$
\end_inset

 变化，则
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathrm{\delta}S=\pdv{S}{\underline{q}(t_{2})}\cdot\mathopen{\mathrm{\delta}}\underline{q}(t_{2})+\pdv{S}{\underline{q}(t_{1})}\cdot\mathopen{\mathrm{\delta}}\underline{q}(t_{1})=\int_{t_{1}}^{t_{2}}\left(\pdv{L}{\underline{q}}-\dv{}{t}\pdv{L}{\underline{\dot{q}}}\right)\cdot\mathopen{\mathrm{\delta}}\underline{q}\dd{t}+\left(\pdv{L}{\underline{\dot{q}}}\cdot\mathopen{\mathrm{\delta}}\underline{q}\right)_{t_{1}}^{t_{2}}
\]

\end_inset

真实轨道应满足 Lagrange's 方程，故被积函数为零；边界项中的偏导数可以用广义动量替换，因此有
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathrm{\delta}S=\underline{p}(t_{2})\cdot\mathopen{\mathrm{\delta}}\underline{q}(t_{2})-\underline{p}(t_{1})\cdot\mathopen{\mathrm{\delta}}\underline{q}(t_{1})
\]

\end_inset

比较系数，即得
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\underline{p}(t_{2})=+\pdv{S}{\underline{q}(t_{2})}\qquad\underline{p}(t_{1})=-\pdv{S}{\underline{q}(t_{1})}
\]

\end_inset

将上式代入
\color blue
关于 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{2},t_{1}$
\end_inset

 全导数
\color inherit
（依次固定 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{1},t_{2}$
\end_inset

 并利用变上、下限积分的导数公式）
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dv{S}{t_{2}}=+L(t_{2})=\pdv{S}{t_{2}}+\pdv{S}{\underline{q}(t_{2})}\cdot\underline{\dot{q}}(t_{2})\qquad\dv{S}{t_{1}}=-L(t_{1})=\pdv{S}{t_{1}}+\pdv{S}{\underline{q}(t_{1})}\cdot\underline{\dot{q}}(t_{1})
\]

\end_inset

并利用 
\begin_inset Formula $H=\underline{p}\cdot\underline{\dot{q}}-L$
\end_inset

，可得
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\pdv{S}{t_{2}}=-H(t_{2})\qquad\pdv{S}{t_{1}}=+H(t_{1})
\]

\end_inset

将它们代回
\color blue
关于 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{2},t_{1}$
\end_inset

 全导数
\color inherit
，即得
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dv{S}{t_{2}}=+\underline{p}(t_{2})\cdot\underline{\dot{q}}(t_{2})-H(t_{2})\qquad\dv{S}{t_{1}}=-\underline{p}(t_{1})\cdot\underline{\dot{q}}(t_{1})+H(t_{1})
\]

\end_inset

作用量 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathopen{S}\left(\underline{q}(t_{1}),\underline{q}(t_{2}),t_{1},t_{2}\right)$
\end_inset

 的全微分（允许 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{1},t_{2}$
\end_inset

 一起变化）应当是这两个微商与各自时间微元的乘积之和，即
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{\mathopen{\dd{S}}\left(\underline{q}(t_{1}),\underline{q}(t_{2}),t_{1},t_{2}\right)=\left(\underline{p}(t)\cdot\mathopen{\dd{\underline{q}}}(t)-H(t)\dd{t}\right)_{t_{1}}^{t_{2}}}
\]

\end_inset

该式表明：真实轨道必须使右端表达式为全微分。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
微分与积分形式
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
特别地，若取定初始位置（即 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathopen{\mathrm{\delta}}\underline{q}(t_{1})=0$
\end_inset

）并省略 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{2}$
\end_inset

 的下标，则有
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dd{S}=\underline{p}\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}-H\dd{t}\implies\boxed{S=\int\left(\underline{p}\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}-H\dd{t}\right)}
\]

\end_inset

将 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{p},\underline{q}$
\end_inset

 视为 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

 的独立变量，利用最小作用量原理 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{\delta}S=0$
\end_inset

，可重新导出 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand nameref
reference "sec:Hamilton's-方程"

\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Maupertuis' 原理
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
只考虑满足
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand nameref
reference "sec:Hamiltonian-能量守恒"

\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $H(\underline{p},\underline{q})=E$
\end_inset

 的系统。若取定初始时刻 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{0}$
\end_inset

 及始末位置 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{q}(t_{0}),\underline{q}(t)$
\end_inset

 且允许终止时刻 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

 变化，则有
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathrm{\delta}S=-H(\underline{p},\underline{q})\,\mathrm{\delta}t=-E\,\mathrm{\delta}t
\]

\end_inset

另一方面，对作用量的 Hamiltonian 形式
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S=-(t-t_{0})E+\int_{t_{0}}^{t}\underline{p}\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}
\]

\end_inset

作变分，可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathrm{\delta}S=-E\,\mathrm{\delta}t+\mathrm{\delta}S_{0}\qquad S_{0}\coloneqq\int_{t_{0}}^{t}\underline{p}\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $S_{0}$
\end_inset

 被称为
\color blue
简约作用量
\color inherit
。消去 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{\delta}S=-E\,\mathrm{\delta}t$
\end_inset

，就得到 
\color blue
Maupertuis' 原理
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathrm{\delta}S_{0}\equiv\boxed{\mathrm{\delta}{\int_{t_{0}}^{t}\underline{p}\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}}=0}
\]

\end_inset

基于该原理，可以解出
\color blue
轨道
\color inherit
，即不含时间的曲线方程。具体做法如下：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
由 
\begin_inset Formula $E=E(\underline{q},\underline{\dot{q}})$
\end_inset

 解出 
\begin_inset Formula $\dd{t}$
\end_inset

，将 
\begin_inset Formula $\dd{t}$
\end_inset

 表示成以 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{q},\dd{\underline{q}}$
\end_inset

 为自变量的函数。 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
将上述 
\begin_inset Formula $\dd{t}$
\end_inset

 代入 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{p}=\partial L/\mathopen{\partial}\underline{\dot{q}}$
\end_inset

，将 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{p}$
\end_inset

 也表示成以 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{q},\dd{\underline{q}}$
\end_inset

 为自变量的函数。 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
将上述 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{p}$
\end_inset

 代入 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{\delta}S_{0}=0$
\end_inset

，即得 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{q},\dd{\underline{q}}$
\end_inset

 所应满足的方程，此即
\color blue
轨道方程
\color inherit
。 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
对于典型系统
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
L=\tfrac{1}{2}\underline{\dot{q}}\cdot\underline{A}(\underline{q})\cdot\underline{\dot{q}}-U(\underline{q})\qquad\underline{p}=\underline{\dot{q}}\cdot\underline{A}(\underline{q})\qquad E=\tfrac{1}{2}\underline{\dot{q}}\cdot\underline{A}(\underline{q})\cdot\underline{\dot{q}}+U(\underline{q})
\]

\end_inset

上述步骤给出
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\dd{t}=\sqrt{\frac{\underline{q}\cdot\underline{A}(\underline{q})\cdot\underline{q}}{2(E-U(\underline{q}))}} & \implies\underline{p}\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}=\frac{\dd{\underline{q}}\cdot\underline{A}(\underline{q})\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}}{\dd{t}}=\sqrt{2(E-U(\underline{q}))\dd{\underline{q}}\cdot\underline{A}(\underline{q})\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}}\\
 & \implies\boxed{\mathrm{\delta}\int_{t_{0}}^{t}\sqrt{2(E-U(\underline{q}))\dd{\underline{q}}\cdot\underline{A}(\underline{q})\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}}=0}
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
正则变换
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
正则变换条件
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
一般的变量替换
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\underline{\tilde{q}}=\underline{\tilde{q}}(\underline{q},\underline{p},t)\qquad\underline{\tilde{p}}=\underline{\tilde{p}}(\underline{q},\underline{p},t)
\]

\end_inset

不能保证新的运动方程仍具有正则形式，即
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\underline{\dot{\tilde{q}}}=+\pdv{\tilde{H}}{\underline{\tilde{p}}}\qquad\underline{\dot{\tilde{p}}}=-\pdv{\tilde{H}}{\underline{\tilde{q}}}
\]

\end_inset

但满足如下条件
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{\left(\exists F\right)\left(\dd{F}=\dd{S}-\dd{\tilde{S}}\right)}\qquad\begin{cases}
\dd{S}=\underline{p}\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}-H\dd{t}\\
\dd{\tilde{S}}=\underline{\tilde{p}}\cdot\dd{\underline{\tilde{q}}}-\tilde{H}\dd{t}
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

的变换能够保持方程的正则性，因此该条件被称为
\color blue
正则变换条件
\color inherit
，其中 
\begin_inset Formula $F=F(\underline{q},\underline{p},\underline{\tilde{q}},\underline{\tilde{p}},t)$
\end_inset

 被称为该变换的
\color blue
生成函数
\color inherit
。这是因为，变换前后的作用量 
\begin_inset Formula $S,\tilde{S}$
\end_inset

 能分别导出 Hamilton's 方程，并且二者之差 
\begin_inset Formula $S-\tilde{S}=\left.F\right|_{t_{1}}^{t_{2}}$
\end_inset

 为不影响变分的常数。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
正则变换公式
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
将正则变换条件
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dd{F}=\underline{p}\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}-\underline{\tilde{p}}\cdot\dd{\underline{\tilde{q}}}+(\tilde{H}-H)\dd{t}
\]

\end_inset

与全微分
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dd{F}=\pdv{F}{\underline{q}}\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}+\pdv{F}{\underline{\tilde{q}}}\cdot\dd{\underline{\tilde{q}}}+\pdv{F}{t}\dd{t}
\]

\end_inset

比较系数，可得第一种正则变换公式：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{\underline{p}=\pdv{F}{\underline{q}}\qquad\underline{\tilde{p}}=-\pdv{F}{\underline{\tilde{q}}}\qquad\tilde{H}-H=\pdv{F}{t}}
\]

\end_inset

其中生成函数 
\begin_inset Formula $F$
\end_inset

 只依赖于 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{q},\underline{\tilde{q}},t$
\end_inset

；若要获得只依赖于 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{q},\underline{\tilde{p}},t$
\end_inset

 的生成函数，则需对正则变换条件作 Legendre's 变换：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dd{\varPhi}\coloneqq\dd{(F+\underline{\tilde{p}}\cdot\underline{\tilde{q}})}=\underline{p}\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}+\underline{\tilde{q}}\cdot\dd{\underline{\tilde{p}}}+(\tilde{H}-H)\dd{t}
\]

\end_inset

并与全微分
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dd{\varPhi}=\pdv{\varPhi}{\underline{q}}\cdot\dd{\underline{q}}+\pdv{\varPhi}{\underline{\tilde{p}}}\cdot\dd{\underline{\tilde{p}}}+\pdv{\varPhi}{t}\dd{t}
\]

\end_inset

比较系数，由此得第二种正则变换公式：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{\underline{p}=\pdv{\varPhi}{\underline{q}}\qquad\underline{\tilde{q}}=\pdv{\varPhi}{\underline{\tilde{p}}}\qquad\tilde{H}-H=\pdv{\varPhi}{t}}
\]

\end_inset

类似地，可得另外两种母函数及相应的正则变换公式：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dd{G}\coloneqq\dd{(F-\underline{p}\cdot\underline{q})}=-\underline{q}\cdot\dd{\underline{p}}-\underline{\tilde{p}}\cdot\dd{\underline{\tilde{q}}}+(\tilde{H}-H)\dd{t}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{\underline{q}=-\pdv{G}{\underline{p}}\qquad\underline{\tilde{p}}=-\pdv{G}{\underline{\tilde{q}}}\qquad\tilde{H}-H=\pdv{G}{t}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dd{\varPsi}\coloneqq\dd{(\varPhi-\underline{p}\cdot\underline{q})}=-\underline{q}\cdot\dd{\underline{p}}+\underline{\tilde{q}}\cdot\dd{\underline{\tilde{p}}}+(\tilde{H}-H)\dd{t}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{\underline{q}=-\pdv{\varPsi}{\underline{p}}\qquad\underline{\tilde{q}}=\pdv{\varPsi}{\underline{\tilde{p}}}\qquad\tilde{H}-H=\pdv{\varPsi}{t}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
正则共轭变量
\end_layout

\begin_layout Lemma
变换 
\begin_inset Formula $(\underline{\tilde{q}},\underline{\tilde{p}})\coloneqq(\underline{p},-\underline{q})$
\end_inset

 是以 
\begin_inset Formula $F=\underline{q}\cdot\underline{\tilde{q}}$
\end_inset

 为生成函数的正则变换。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由此可见：
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand nameref
reference "sec:Hamilton's-方程"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

中的变量是完全对等的，即：不必区分一个变量是
\color blue
广义坐标
\color inherit
还是
\color blue
广义动量
\color inherit
。具有这种性质的（成对出现的）变量被称为
\color blue
正则共轭变量
\color inherit
。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Liouville's 定理
\end_layout

\begin_layout Lemma
真实运动所引起的正则共轭变量 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{q},\underline{p}$
\end_inset

 的变化，可以看作一系列正则变换累加的结果，即 
\begin_inset Formula $\exists F$
\end_inset

 使得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dd{F}=\left(\underline{p}(t)\cdot\dd{\underline{q}(t)}-H(t)\dd{t}\right)-\left(\underline{p}(t+\tau)\cdot\dd{\underline{q}(t+\tau)}-H(t+\tau)\dd{t}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

